facilities {
  name: "Diane Deans Greenboro Community Centre"
  description:
    "Snuggled in the heart of the Greenboro/South Keys district, the Diane Deans Greenboro Community Centre opens its "
    "doors to welcome all. We offer a wide variety of recreation programs for all ages, stages and interests. There is "
    "a state of the art fitness studio, cardio and weight room, group cycling studio, dance and yoga studio, a full "
    "sized gymnasium ideal for sports and a variety of multi-purpose rooms. Consider renting our spaces for birthday "
    "parties, meetings, sports leagues, and much more. You will also find the Greenboro District Library located "
    "within the facility. Outside, just across Lorry Greenberg Drive, there are public tennis courts and walking "
    "trails and out back is a large park with more walking trails, sports fields, an amazing play structure, and "
    "wading pool. Greenboro Community Centre; it's a great place to be."
  source {
    url: "https://ottawa.ca/en/recreation-and-parks/facilities/place-listing/diane-deans-greenboro-community-centre"
