facilities {
  name: "Hunt Club-Riverside Park Community Centre"
  description:
    "Located in the centre of the community, we offer a wide selection of recreation activities. There are programs "
    "for all ages from preschoolers to seniors with arts and crafts, dance classes, language lessons and fitness "
    "programs just to name a few. The Centre features a full gymnasium, weight room, four multipurpose rooms, a "
    "kitchen and onsite parking. It also hosts an Ottawa Public Library kiosk and the Hunt Club-Riverside Community "
    "Services Centre. Outdoor space includes play structures, a basketball court, baseball diamond, two soccer fields "
    "and a rink."
