facilities {
  name: "Ken Ross Park Field House"
  description:
    "The Ken Ross Field House is located at the back of the parking lot. It offers change rooms, washrooms, a "
    "kitchenette and a small hall. Recreation programs are offered at this location. It is also available for private "
    "rentals. The Field House is surrounded by sports fields, a splash pad and a children's play structure."
