facilities {
  name: "McNabb Arena and Community Centre"
  description:
    "This multipurpose facility offers a wide variety of programs and amenities including an arena, gymnasium, meeting "
    "rooms, dance studio and pottery studio. Located in downtown Ottawa, McNabb Community Centre is located next to "
    "lovely McNabb Park where seasonal activities include a playground, wading pool, outdoor skateboard park (indoor "
    "skateboard park is permanently closed) and an outdoor skating rink."
